mean_cn: n. 超自然物，神奇人物，不可思议的事；  adj. 超自然的
mean_en: unable to be explained by science or the laws of nature :of, relating to, or seeming to come from magic, a god, etc.
word_etyma: super超级 + natural自然的 → supernatural 超自然的
sentence: Corn circles are widely believed to be made by supernatural powers.
sentence_trans: 麦田怪圈被大家认为产生于超自然力量。
